Text:
The theme song from "Welcome Back Kotter" plays in my head. 

Cheers Toyota!
so nice to have you back!!
Is the old hag still alive
I have run out of compliments Wingz. :)
Welcome back! Hope you had a great vacation & thanks for more JJ! :)

WINGZZZZ!!!  Thanks so much.  Perhaps you read the dog next door is missing .. and I'm on house arrest.  So I'm so glad you are back!  I was so bored without you I started to download and watch Wheel of Fortune and subscribed to the National Enquirer. {shudder}

Hi ghdsd,  i have 3 pitbbulls (they dont bite) and im kinda short with cash right now.  

Can i move in with you and borrow $3000?  I'll pay you back the loan & rent , i promise.

Hi Back NimH - sure .... as in Price is Right .. "Come on down!"  I trust you to pay back the loan too, you have a nice font.  I don't care if your dogs bite, only barking INCESSANTLY right out side of my window bothers me.... like that sweet doggie that used to live right next door to me.  I hope you will enjoy Wyoming!
